      <title>随着投资者资金流入，花旗金价有望触及 3,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/gold-seen-hitting-3-000-at-citi-as-investor-inflows-juice-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团表示，在美联储最终降息的预期下，随着投资者资金流入的增加，金价将在未来 6 至 18 个月内达到每盎司 3,000 美元，而华尔街银行也已上调了预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/gold-seen-hitting-3-000-at-citi-as-investor-inflows-juice-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 05:17:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
