    <item>
      <title>由于通胀风险，菲律宾 2025 年降息的可能性更大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/philippine-central-bank-chief-sees-rate-cut-more-likely-in-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾央行行长雷莫洛纳 (Eli Remolona) 表示，随着通胀可能连续第三年突破目标的风险上升，菲律宾央行在 2024 年下半年开始降低关键利率的窗口正在缩小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/philippine-central-bank-chief-sees-rate-cut-more-likely-in-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 12:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
